column5: Are you wondering why the fish are not biting?
Good one.not much covid in canada so there not weating masks here and good bite

Greetings, My friend pointed out that the fish in the picture was not in a school with other fish - must have been practicing social distancing. I had a good friend that frequently traveled to South Korea. He is an avid angler. He took a traveler's spinning rod with him on one of his many trips. Over a weekend, he and his business contacts went to a lake such that he could fish from shore. His first catch was a large mouth bass. He found out that the fish were planted there shortly after the Korean War to provide a food source for local people. Maybe they are in China? Kindest Regards....
